summary:
ABOUT - Named after the beloved Dave Portnoy’s dog Miss Peaches, our token is more than just an asset – it’s a symbol of hope and generosity.

 CHARITY - In a paw-sitively inspiring move, Miss Peaches is using her newfound fame to launch a crypto charity project. She’s not just sitting pretty in the penthouse; she’s sharing the wealth with her fellow furry friends in need

 TOKENOMICS - All post launch tax is going to charity.
